(3\) Sizing Units \(px, %, rem, vw\)) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(- px: fixed size \(good for borders, icon sizes\).) Tj
T*
(- %: relative to parent size.) Tj
T*
(- rem: relative to root font size \(great for scalable typography\).) Tj
T*
(- vw / vh: relative to viewport.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Example:) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(```css) Tj
T*
(.title {) Tj
T*
