( ) Tj
T*
(Important properties) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(- display: flex) Tj
T*
(- justify-content: horizontal distribution in row mode) Tj
T*
(- align-items: vertical alignment in row mode) Tj
T*
(- flex-wrap: wrap: allows next line when space is tight) Tj
T*
(- gap: clean spacing between items) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Example \(desktop row that wraps on mobile\):) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(```css) Tj
T*
(.main-row {) Tj
T*
(    display: flex;) Tj
T*
(    justify-content: center;) Tj
T*
(    align-items: stretch;) Tj
T*
(    flex-wrap: wrap;) Tj
T*
(    gap: 24px;) Tj
T*
(}) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Understanding flex: 1 1 320px) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(- First 1: can grow) Tj
T*
(- Second 1: can shrink) Tj
T*
(- 320px: preferred base width) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Example card sizing:) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(```css) Tj
T*
(.card-large {) Tj
T*
(    flex: 1 1 620px;) Tj
T*
(}) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(.card-small {) Tj
T*
(    flex: 1 1 320px;) Tj
T*
(}) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
